data.text:
Description

Black and white photograph depicting Crown Prince Olav and Crown Princess Martha of Norway being escorted to the Grand Ballroom by Oscar Tschirky, where they were guests of honor at a state banquet given by the Committee for Norway's Participation in the New York World's Fair, May 2, 1939.
